author: desruisseaux
msg: Start using the Identifier <-> TypeName mapping in ServiceParameter.
An open issue in this commit is the fact that ISO 19139 does not include the namespace of TypeName objects in XML document,
so we currently fail to infer the java.lang.Class from an unmarshalled XML TypeName because of the missing "OGC" or "class" namespace.
